This is a project developed as part of the second course of Java Specialization at Coursera.org

Specialization name: "Java Programming: Object-Oriented Design of Data Structures" by UC San Diego.
URL: https://www.coursera.org/specializations/java-object-oriented
Course name: "Data structures: Measuring and Optimizing Performance"

Implemented:  
1. How easy to read is the input text? : Calculating Flesch Index of the input text.  
2. Markov chain text generator. (https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Markov_chain)  
3. Spell Check and Auto Complete  
4. Spelling suggestions  
5. Word paths  
